NAME: Cindi Dong


This project contains C code and a Makefile for running Grove Sensors (temperature sensor) on an embedded system.


Included Files:
lab4b.c: C source files for an embedded application that builds and runs on an embedded system
Makefile: 4 targets
-default: compiles lab4b with the flags -g -Wall -Wextra -lmraa -lm
-check: executes an automated smoke-test of your application to see if it runs and can talk to its sensors
-dist: creates compressed tarball with lab4b.c, Makefile, and README
-clean: removes files created by Makefile

Extra Files:
-tests: Bash tests for my make check target. Checks exit code of the program and if the program logged START, STOP, LOG, SCALE, PERIOD, OFF, and SHUTDOWN correctly.


Sources Used:
https://www.tutorialspoint.com/c_standard_library/c_function_localtime.htm
geeksforgeeks.org/time-function-in-c/
